<div id="review_78732032" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/78732032" />
    <a title="Clara Roberts" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1974067-clara-roberts"><img alt="Clara Roberts" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/78732032?book_show_action=true">Nov 23, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Clara Roberts" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Clara Roberts" href="/user/show/1974067-clara-roberts">Clara Roberts</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer78732032" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11668959885072819155">The book was a fascinating read of Arab and Islamic culture. The Arabs refused to do more than the miniumun amount of work and therefore were amazed to see the hard work of the Jews and some Europeans. This was 566 pages of Arabs sitting around in squalor complaining and expecting someone to come and rescue them. There seemed to be no iniative or ambition to do anything on their own. They had them same resources available to them that the Jews had but lacked any work ethic. Whereas the Jews abso</span>
  <span id="freeText11668959885072819155" style="display:none">The book was a fascinating read of Arab and Islamic culture. The Arabs refused to do more than the miniumun amount of work and therefore were amazed to see the hard work of the Jews and some Europeans. This was 566 pages of Arabs sitting around in squalor complaining and expecting someone to come and rescue them. There seemed to be no iniative or ambition to do anything on their own. They had them same resources available to them that the Jews had but lacked any work ethic. Whereas the Jews absorbed their refuges into the larger Jewish society, the Arabs rejected their refugees leaving them in camps to be fed and cared for by American and European largess. No Arab country gave for the needs of fellow Arabs. The Arabs in the book had an almost incomprehensible obssession with sex. Sex of every variey was mentioned. After reading this book it is hard to look on Muslim Arabs with anything but disgust. This is supposed to be a well researched book of historical fiction. If that is true then Muslim Arabs are disgusting. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11668959885072819155" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
