          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Perhaps the bazaar looks disorganized to you, but it works for us. Perhaps Islam looks fanatical to you, but it provides us with the means to survive the harshness of this life and prepare us for a better life hereafter.&rdquo;</span>
